Version 0.4.1

* Split dlwrap headers to separate package.

Version 0.4

* Reimplementation of the wrapper. Now the wrapper is more generic and
  allows to define arbitrary actions.
* Writes "DLWRAP:" instead of "WRAP:".

Version 0.3

* Support for wrapping gettext.
* Incompatible change: Encloses strings in quotes.


Version 0.2

* Fix linking with -ldl.
